comments: Vielen Dank und Grüße aus dem Saarland😊! Das Video war ein prima Begleiter für die Indoor-Tour !
Great ride.  A beautiful view while I’m buried in snow in Canada.

❤ very scenic good pace and endless blue sky . Thank you!!! Im almost 70. Cycling this way with a good video is wonderul all you young making these videos are doing us older folks the best gift ever. 26:47
A well paced hour on my bike. Thank you for all your wonderful videos.

Absolutely amazing. This guy is so generous with his time to put the tech and video together. Indoor cycling (for me) has never been such fun until now. I’d love to be where he is on my road bike, but until then this will be my go to place. (Bit surprised by what looked like close passes on these lovely roads - maybe it’s just camera angles) . Thanks , keep it up. I will tip.
